
// This Hyperlambda code snippet uses the [strings.replace] slot to replace occurrences of "{{reset_link}}" in the string referenced by [@.reset-email] with the value obtained from [@.arguments/*/reset_link]. The [strings.replace] slot facilitates dynamic string manipulation by substituting placeholders with actual values, allowing for flexible and customizable string content.
strings.replace:x:@.reset-email
   .:{{reset_link}}
   get-value:x:@.arguments/*/reset_link
